contestDescription: Unleash your entrepreneurial spirit in the Business Innovation Challenge. Propose innovative business solutions and compete for recognition!
taskSubmissionText: Submit a detailed proposal outlining your innovative business idea and its potential impact.

contestDescription: Contribute to medical research in the Medical Research Symposium. Present groundbreaking findings and advance healthcare!
taskSubmissionText: Submit a research paper highlighting your medical findings, methodology, and potential impact on healthcare.

contestDescription: Explore the world of words in the Creative Writing Extravaganza. Craft compelling stories and showcase your literary prowess!
taskSubmissionText: Submit an original piece of creative writing, whether it's a short story, poem, or essay, expressing your unique perspective.

contestDescription: Showcase your gaming skills in the Gaming Tournament. Compete against the best and emerge victorious!
taskSubmissionText: Participate in a thrilling gaming tournament. Submit your gameplay videos and achievements to demonstrate your gaming prowess.

contestDescription: Address environmental challenges in the Environmental Sustainability Challenge. Propose sustainable solutions for a better future!
taskSubmissionText: Submit a proposal outlining your sustainable solution to a specific environmental challenge. Emphasize the potential positive impact.

contestDescription: Innovate in the Tech Innovation Hackathon. Develop groundbreaking tech solutions and push the boundaries of innovation!
taskSubmissionText: Submit a working prototype of your tech innovation along with documentation detailing its features and potential applications.
